          <td height="45" VALIGN="TOP" bgcolor="#333333"><div class="topictitle"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=100%>
      <tr>
       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">SOE FanFaire Atlanta 2006</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Fricka - Safehouse Contributing Editor, Forums Admin</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Apr 10, 2006, 15:12</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=SOE%20FanFaire%20Atlanta%202006&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Fevents%2Farticle_49.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
